27
00:03:32,678 --> 00:03:34,138
Michuri Public Health Center.

28
00:03:35,055 --> 00:03:38,100
Hiking... Hiking Trail Entrance.
Oeryong Bridge.

29
00:03:38,184 --> 00:03:39,935
Stop memorizing that.
Go wash up, Sang-tae.

30
00:03:42,563 --> 00:03:46,066
