843
01:03:39,169 --> 01:03:40,253
What did I do?

844
01:03:41,505 --> 01:03:43,298
You helped her cut herself free.

845
01:04:13,537 --> 01:04:14,579
You will

846
01:04:18,208 --> 01:04:20,836
