847
01:04:22,212 --> 01:04:26,091
You won't be able to escape.

848
01:04:28,802 --> 01:04:29,636
No.

849
01:04:31,471 --> 01:04:32,514
I'm different.

850
01:05:46,880 --> 01:05:47,964
Your...

851
01:05:50,008 --> 01:05:51,593
-Your hair--
-I...

852
01:05:52,427 --> 01:05:53,887
cut off my leash.

